Xiaopi,

856
00:43:01,480 --> 00:43:02,960
lead this girl to the backyard.

857
00:43:03,680 --> 00:43:04,600
Yes. Follow me, please.

858
00:43:04,920 --> 00:43:06,080
-Go on.
-Thank you.

859
00:43:06,840 --> 00:43:07,800
Thank you.

860
00:43:31,600 --> 00:43:33,000
How much money can you make

861
00:43:33,160 --> 00:43:34,240
