in the name of teaching,

884
00:44:15,840 --> 00:44:17,440
Xianling Pavilion

885
00:44:17,560 --> 00:44:18,640
is exploiting your labor.

886
00:44:18,720 --> 00:44:20,360
You can't put it this way.

887
00:44:20,560 --> 00:44:21,880
-Exactly.
-Exactly.

888
00:44:22,280 --> 00:44:23,760
Without Master Jian,

889
00:44:23,880 --> 00:44:25,400
