00:44:44,520 --> 00:44:45,560
Exactly.

899
00:44:45,680 --> 00:44:47,320
It is impossible for

900
00:44:47,440 --> 00:44:48,040
Master Jian and Master Luo

901
00:44:48,160 --> 00:44:49,440
to do such evil deeds.

902
00:44:49,640 --> 00:44:50,560
Right.

