00:44:50,680 --> 00:44:51,640
We can all see clearly that

904
00:44:51,760 --> 00:44:52,560
Master Jian and Master Luo

905
00:44:52,680 --> 00:44:53,840
treat us kindly.

906
00:44:53,960 --> 00:44:55,200
Stop talking irresponsibly.

907
00:45:37,140 --> 00:45:40,860
♪In the cold darkness of midnight,
